ests.\n32 DEAD, 72 HURT IN\nGERMAN MINE DISASTER\nBERLIN, June 21. - Thirty-two\nminers are dead, fourteen are missing\nand seventy-two are suffering from\ngas poisoning as the result of a dis¬\naster in the Stinnes coal mine near\nHerne, today.&quot;, &quot;line_offsets&quot;: [[0, 20], [21, 40], [41, 74], [75, 107], [108, 141], [142, 176], [177, 211], [212, 248], [249, 280], [281, 316], [317, 351], [352, 381], [382, 413], [414, 447], [448, 483], [484, 494], [495, 514], [515, 535], [536, 565], [566, 603], [604, 638], [639, 676], [677, 712], [713, 726]], &quot;sentence_offsets&quot;: [[0, 248], [249, 386], [387, 494], [495, 726]], &quot;num_tokens&quot;: 108, &quot;num_chars&quot;: 726, &quot;quality_report&quot;: {&quot;ocr_quality_score&quot;: 0.98}}, &quot;ocr_hypothesis&quot;: {&quot;transcription_unit&quot;: &quot;SPARROWS ATTACK MEN;\nMAKE THEM QUIT WORil\nDANVILLE Pa.. June 21.-Sparrow\npecking at the faces and eyes o\nworkmen who were trying to repal\nthe slate roof on the tower of Ma\nhoning Presbyterian Church. force4\nthem to descend and give up the Joib\nHundreds of the birds had thel\nnests in the old tower, and sulphu\nwas being used to exterminate then\nwhen they swooped down on thi\nmen. &#39;Tustees of the church ar\nconsidering offering a reward for\nsuccessful method of getting rid o\nthe pests.\n32 DEAD, 72 HURT IN\nGERMAN MINE DISASTEF\nR1FRLTN, JVune 21. - Thirty-twe\nminers are desd, fourteen are misin\nand seventy-two are suffering froni\ngas poisoning as the result of a dis\naster in the Stinnes coal mine near\nMamae todaR_&quot;, &quot;line_offsets&quot;: [[0, 20], [21, 41], [42, 72], [73, 104], [105, 137], [138, 171], [172, 206], [207, 243], [244, 274], [275, 309], [310, 344], [345, 374], [375, 405], [406, 439], [440, 474], [475, 485], [486, 505], [506, 526], [527, 558], [559, 594], [595, 630], [631, 667], [668, 703], [704, 716]], &quot;sentence_offsets&quot;: [[0, 243], [244, 379], [380, 485], [486, 716]], &quot;num_tokens&quot;: 106, &qu